        <abstract>
            <p>For CD’s approval, cites passage from CD note he wants to quote in a lecture;</p>
            <p>pleads for CD’s moral support for FEA’s work in free-thought movement.</p> 
<p>Sends $50 [dollars or pounds!?] because he wants CD to become regular contributor to <hi rend="italic">Index</hi>.</p> 
        </abstract>
